    "In the second round, out-of-scope articles and review articles are filtered by reading the title, abstract, and conclusion sections.",
    "In the third round, the articles are subjected to quality evaluation.",
    "The quality evaluation is conducted according to the checklist items defined by Ekman [91] that can be seen in Table 5.",
    "In the fourthround articles are again evaluated regarding the following inclusion criteria (1) the study is limited to only English-language and human subjects' studies; (2) includes Does the study make use of cross-sectional or time series statistical (descriptive/non-parametric) analysis, incl.",
    "significance levels in relevant sections?"
